{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/UncoverTheTruth.gif?t=1733132236\" /><br>Step into the eerie world of '[ANOMALY TAPES]: Beyond Reality,' a retro analog horror game that takes you on a spine-chilling journey through a series of events. Each tape you find brings you closer to uncovering a dark secret, but beware\u2014the anomalies are always lurking.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/Wendy2.gif?t=1733132236\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/GameplayFeatures.gif?t=1733132236\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore:</strong> Navigate through 8 main levels, each filled with unique challenges and atmospheric horror.<br></li><li><strong>Survive:</strong> Use a handheld camera perspective to document your journey and avoid deadly anomalies that stalk you relentlessly.<br></li><li><strong>Adapt:</strong> Each entity you encounter has unique gameplay mechanics. Learn and adapt quickly to survive the different challenges posed by each entity.<br></li><li><strong>Discover:</strong> Piece together the story behind the anomalies and your connection to them. Not everything is as it seems.<br></li><li><strong>Analyze:</strong> Replay the game to uncover subtle clues and hidden details that reveal the truth behind this place.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/YouHurtUs.gif?t=1733132236\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/StoryLine.gif?t=1733132236\" /><br>In a world where reality bends and twists, you are thrust into something sinister. As you navigate a series of haunting environments, each more disturbing than the last, document your journey along the way. But be careful\u2014each step forward brings you closer to a terrifying revelation.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/HeWatched.gif?t=1733132236\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/Can_You_Escape.gif?t=1733132236\" /><br>As you delve deeper into the mystery, you'll find yourself questioning your own sanity. What dark secrets lie beyond the tapes? '[ANOMALY TAPES]: Beyond Reality' invites you to explore, survive, and uncover the truth\u2014if you dare.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145780/extras/IFoundYou.gif?t=1733132236\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Tape 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3145780/deae4fbde769ac528faeb4b56e78305278feeca4.jpg"},{"name":"Speed run Tape 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3145780/fa00ec229747b15e20c415626fca057e235ec70a.jpg"},{"name":"Tape 1...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3145780/8e063e820f7863140d3a8fa2bb69e1bd5592de35.jpg"},{"name":"Tape 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3145780/cb756dc41af036cae8248e85bb4040330c52be4f.jpg"},{"name":"Speed run Tape 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3145780/e2f6b1c54a9b1b59bae48d346cbee746a29bf518.jpg"},{"name":"Tape 2...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3145780/a06fc2a569ef84283e43a2cf94c11ef0575b87c4.jpg"},{"name":"Tape 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3145780/2debe2232b13ce6d5975208487b32abfa1c4e66a.jpg"},{"name":"Speed run Tape 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/31